{"tid":102553,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩辦法說服我呀嫲過層樓俾我","createTime":"2017-01-31T17:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T18:33:27.000Z","uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ee62cc8dbbd22a8b9fad41a2e165c0d7229cddd8","tid":102553,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:02:04.000Z","msg":"呢位親戚無事無幹個陣呢<br />\n<br />\n對我地一家唔揪唔彩<br />\n<br />\n我老豆有事個陣佢唔幫手，叫佢自己搞掂。<br />\n<br />\n我兩老結婚個陣呢就昆我呀媽話有瓦遮頭俾佢地<br />\n<br />\n最後一拖再拖，佢地租左十年樓先反口話無講過，咁咩婚前儲錢計劃呀，首期當然無儲，貿貿然無足夠儲蓄下生左我出黎。<br />\n<br />\n到我細個個時，有次食飯唔小心叫錯佢做婆婆 就十年無搵過我（仲唔俾我去拜年）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說佢近年病到好嚴重，個人恰下恰下先醒係有我依個呀孫<br />\n<br />\n話想我多啲陪佢，見下臉食下飯<br />\n<br />\n成日搵藉口過錢俾我洗 又叫我上去佢屋企過夜陪下佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問題黎啦，我依個乖孫想幫佢積下陰德，幫佢守番對我一家既承諾<br />\n<br />\n想問下可以點動之以情說服佢過層單位黎呢？"},{"pid":"540dabbf4fbc9ef9ea0290c503b8c6fd2b841bb7","tid":102553,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:03:33.000Z","msg":"少女唔鋤愛阿婆"},{"pid":"7d923dcf68f5d1bd1c065d959982d3c2fd207d6f","tid":102553,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:04:54.000Z","msg":"離間任何人"},{"pid":"1f1f226fe81ce58c1419188a00c38cf9b4254614","tid":102553,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T17:04:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>少女唔鋤愛阿婆</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f189219d06ed86fc57ce4fa9e74b057084f665","tid":102553,"uid":69578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:14:57.000Z","msg":"同佢講：你比層樓我 我幫你全家祈福"},{"pid":"d9b9423fe2a2af17531b15ecf8cc49cb370c8537","tid":102553,"uid":33505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:22:49.000Z","msg":"不如你去感情台開返個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝早日上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3f50bd096a4c3885cfa1cff9465b28d6476af1","tid":102553,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:26:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如你去感情台開返個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝早日上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf77574bae25f4178b297fbfbdec6bf4d18f72e","tid":102553,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:33:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[black]<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">成日搵藉口過錢俾我洗 又叫我上去佢<span style=\"color: red;\">屋企過夜</span></strong>[/black]</span>陪下佢咁</blockquote><br />\n為層樓去咁盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}